VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'prompt and the settings are the same basically for all of them. I might have changed the animation amplitude from auto to small, medium, or large, but I just want you to get an idea of the quality of the output that we\'ve got going here. So, I tried all kinds of prompts. Some of them I can\'t show you'

[03:25] [scene:talk]
