VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'number generations and create. And while we\'re waiting, I\'ll show you several examples. Remember, all of this functionality is for the Bedu 2.0 model, so we don\'t have the 1080p resolution at this time. Right here, we\'ve got a 720p image. I\'ve combined the reference of'

[15:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Tracy and the reference of Tess, and they\'re doing a photo shoot in Times Square. Here, they\'re doing a photo shoot in a cornfield. Here, I combine my character reference with an image of this mushroom guy in a forest, and it'

